<P><B>MUELLER, LOUIS J. - </B>93, of Morristown, passed away Sunday morning, January 19, 1997, at his residence following a lengthy illness. Mr. Mueller was a member of Centenary United Methodist Church. He was preceded in death by: son, Rev. William F. Mueller; and wife, Mildred E. Mueller. Survivors: son, Dr. Robert L. Mueller and his wife, Dorothy, Knoxville; nine grandchildren; five great-grandchildren; and one great-great-grandchild; special friend, Brenda Smith and other loving caregivers. Funeral services 2 p.m. Tuesday, January 21, in Stetzer&#39;s Chapel with the Rev. Dwight Kenney officiating. Interment Hamblen Memory Gardens. The family will receive friends 7-9 p.m. today at Stetzer Funeral Home in Morristown. Friends wishing to express sympathy may do so through memorial donations to ALPS of Morristown. Stetzer Funeral Home, in charge of arrangements.
