<P><B>LeROY, ADA PAULINE (JOHNSON) - </B>66, of Bradenton, died January 15, 1997, in Bradenton. A memorial service will be held on Monday at 10 a.m. at St. Joseph&#39;s Catholic Church, 3100 26th St. W., with Father Carmelo Cadarso officiating. Memorial contributions may be made to St. Joseph&#39;s or to Hospice of Southwest Florida, 6055 Rand Blvd., Sarasota, FL 34238. Born in Knoxville, Tenn., she came to Manatee County from Norfolf, Va. in 1968. She was a devoted wife and mother and a devout Catholic. She is survived by: her husband, William; two sons, William and Michael, both of Bradenton; and four grandchildren, Michael and Gregory LeRoy, and Gregory and Kimberly Sons, all of Bradenton. Arrangements are being made by Griffith-Cline Funeral Home, Manasota Chapel.
