<P><B>SAAH, PAULA SUE - </B>age 31, of Knoxville, passed away at 9:27 a.m. Thursday at St. Mary&#39;s Medical Center. She was a member of Holy Ghost Catholic Church. Survived by husband, Adel Saah; sons, John Lee and Adam Adel Saah; father, Paul Wright; mother, Birdie Wright; sister and brother-in-law, Peggy and Joe Greene; brother and sister-in-law, Kenny and Carlene Hill; brother, Bobby Hill; mother and father-in-law, John and Dalal Saah; sister-in-law and brother-in-law, Ruba and Joe Saah; several nieces and nephews; and a host of other relatives and friends. Funeral Mass 10 a.m. Monday at Holy Ghost Catholic Church with Father John Dowling officiating.  Interment will be in Greenwood Cemetery. The family will receive friends 7-9 p.m. Sunday with an 8:30 p.m. Rosary service at Rose Mortuary Broadway Chapel.
