<P>* Receptionist, 50 words per minute typing, computer, four years&#39; experience, high school graduate, minimum age 30, $275 a week, permanent full time, 7012824.
<P>* Carpenter construction, tools, three years&#39; experience, high school graduate, minimum age 21, $10 to $14 an hour, permanent full time, 7012815.
<P>* Production machine operator, some experience, high school graduate, minimum age 18, $9.70 to $9.84 an hour, temporary full time, 7012819.
<P>* Maintenance worker, petroleum depot, high school graduate, minimum age 18, $9 an hour, permanent part time, 7012823.
<P>* Production machine operator, some experience, high school graduate, minimum age 18, $8.88 an hour, permanent full time, 7012820.
<P>* Plant production worker, high school graduate, minimum age 18, $8.87 an hour, permanent full time, 7012827.
<P>* Medical technician, one year&#39;s experience, high school graduate, minimum age 18, $8 an hour, permanent part time, 7012799.
<P>* Office assistant, Word/Excel, two years&#39; experience, associate&#39;s degree, minimum age 21, $8 an hour, permanent full time, 7012830.
<P>* Administrative assistant, Word Perfect, five years&#39; experience, some college, minimum age 25, $7.50 an hour, permanent part time, 7012825.
