<P><B>FORD, MRS. MARTHA L. - </B>age 92, of LaFollette, died Saturday at LaFollette Medical Center. Preceded in death by parents, John and Katie (Housley) Miller; and daughter, Edna Ford Petree. Survivors: daughters, Marie Ramiez, Burbank, Calif., Katherine Hamrick, Cabot, Ark., Dorothy Smith, LaFollette, Grace White, LaFollette, Margaret Gibson, LaFollette; sons, Jennings Ford, Atlanta, Ga., Ray Ford, Pennington Gap, Va.; 34 grandchildren; 41 great-grandchildren. Services 8 p.m. Monday, Roach Memorial Chapel, Rev. Leonard Dabney officiating. Interment 11 a.m. Tuesday in the Pond Cemetery. The family will receive friends 6-8 p.m. Monday at Roach Mortuary, LaFollette.
