<P><B>GRUBB, MRS. EDNA COOPER - </B>age 81, of Corryton, died 1:34 p.m. Sunday, January 12, 1997, at Fort Sanders Regional Medical Center. Member of Corryton Baptist Church. Survivors: husband, Ross Grubb, Corryton; daughter, Ann Pierce and three grandchildren. Funeral arrangements are incomplete. Stevens Mortuary, Oglewood Avenue at Broadway, in charge.
