<P><B>GREEN, LORENE KING - </B>age 89, of Knoxville, died Wednesday, January 8, 1997 at her home. Member of Sequoyah Hills Presbyterian Church, Sigma Kappa Sorority and Ossoli Circle. Former member of Association of University Women. Received B.S. Degree in education at Vanderbuilt University and later studied at Columbia University, New York City. Preceded in death by Husband, M.E. &#39;&#39;Squiz&#39;&#39; Green. Survivors: Son Henry E. Green and daughter-in-law, Theresa Rogers Green; granddaughters, Elise (Lisa) Green Kern and Laura K. Green. Private graveside service, Dr. William Barron officiating. Family will receive friends 7-9:00 p.m. Friday at Rose Mortuary Mann Heritage Chapel.
