<P><B>STRANGE, MARCUS WAYNE - </B>infant son of Stacey and Stephine Strange of Caryville, Tenn., passed away Monday, January 6, 1997. Survivors: parents; brother, Timothy Ray Strange; paternal grandparents, David and Ruby Strange, Knoxville; maternal grandfather and step-mother, Robert Wayne and Judy Sluder, Knoxville; great-grandmother, Ethel Irene Dills, Knoxville; several aunts, uncles and other relatives. Funeral service 2 p.m. Wednesday, January 8, 1997 at Highland Memorial Funeral Home, Rev. Johnny Ridenour officiating. The interment will be in Highland Memorial Cemetery. The family will receive friends 1-2 p.m. Wednesday at Highland Memorial Funeral Home, 5315 Kingston Pike, 588-0567.
