<P><B>TALLENT, PATRICIA ANN WELCH - </B>age 63, of 2862 Fairview Road, Madisonville, passed away 10:17 a.m. Monday, January 6, 1997, at Blount Memorial Hospital. Daughter of the late Ervin and Marjorie Welch. Survivors: husband, Coy Tallent; daughters and son-in-law, Mary and Ernest Miller, Betty Black; sons and daughter-in-law, Dale and Ruth Tallent, Marty Tallent, all of Madisonville; 11 grandchildren; seven great-grandchildren; sisters, Carolyn Bell, Tellico Plains, Esther Miller, Vonore; brothers, Bob Welch, Athens, Paul and Don Welch, both of Madisonville, Jack Welch, Greenback; several nieces and nephews. Preceded in death by brother, Nick Welch. Funeral 8 p.m. Tuesday, Biereley-Hale Chapel, Rev. Melvin Reagan and Rev. Beecher Miller officiating. Interment 11 a.m. Wednesday, Big Creek Cemetery. Family will receive friends 6-8 p.m. Tuesday at Biereley-Hale Funeral Home, Madisonville.
