<table cellpadding=0 cellspacing=10>
	<tr>
	<td valign=top width=150>
		<i>January 04, 1997</i> 
	</td>
	<td align=left width=470>
            <basefont size=6>
		<FONT SIZE="6"><B>Mora Deaderick, widow of financier, dies at 96</B></font><!--SUBHEAD--><P>
		<FONT size="2"><I></I></FONT><P>
		<FONT SIZE="3"><I></I></FONT><BR>
		</basefont><FONT SIZE="+2">M</FONT>ora Allan Deaderick, widow of former Knoxville financier William V. Deaderick, died Dec. 13 at her home in Spotsylvania, Va. She was 96.
<P>   Mrs. Deaderick, a longtime Knoxvillian, moved to Virginia following the death of her husband in 1977. Mr. Deaderick owned and managed Deaderick & Co., which dealt in real estate, investments and loans, until his retirement in 1974. 
<P>   Mrs. Deaderick was a member of Goshen Baptist Church.
<P>   She is survived by son, J. Richard Allan II of Spotsylvania, Va., and daughter, Patricia Jane Allan of Ormond Beach, Fla.
<P>
<P>
