<P>
<P><B>HUMPHREY, VASCO - </B>age 88, of Halls, passed away Tuesday, December 31, 1996, at Hillcrest North. Preceded in death by wife, Louise Humphrey; and daughter, Betty Hickey. Survived by grandchildren, Linda Hemphill, Robert and Kenneth Hickey; 8 great-grandchildren and 5 great-great-grandchildren; brothers, Ben Earl and Rudoff Humphrey; sisters, Beatrice Weaver, Lucille Whitson, Edna Lofton and Anna Cooper. Funeral service 2:30 p.m. Thursday, Mynatt&#39;s Chapel, Rev. Bill Berry and Rev. Harry Whetsell officiating. Interment Halls Memory Gardens. Pallbearers: Larry Hemphill, Kenneth and Danny Hickey, Jesse Stafford, Ronnie Keys and Raymond Clark. In lieu of flowers, contributions may be made to Alzheimer&#39;s Association, East Tenn. Chapter, 1924 Alcoa Hwy., Knoxville, TN 37920. Arrangements by Mynatt&#39;s.
