<P><h3>Outside Area</h3>
<P>FT. OGLETHORPE, Ga.: <B>Humphrey</B> <B>&#39;&#39;Hump&#39;&#39; Cardin, </B>79.
<P>LAKE CITY, Fla.:  Nellie A. Ferger<B>son, </B>87, formerly of Grainger Co.
